comment.body:
@Yuki2718 Thank you for the reply!
I found these domains being made from my smart TVs when I was monitoring all DNS queries made by my devices as I always do. 
As for the proof, I do have logs of the queries in my NextDNS account but I can inspect the packets if you could give me some days.

@gototheskinny Unfortunately, I cannot reproduce this issue. 
Please try to disable-enable content blockers in Safari settings and restart Safari, and check for filters update.
Do not close AdGuard window 30-60 seconds.

